{"id":3340,"date":"2024-12-09T08:28:51","date_gmt":"2024-12-09T08:28:51","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/yoroow.com\/?p=3340"},"modified":"2024-12-09T08:28:52","modified_gmt":"2024-12-09T08:28:52","slug":"how-many-faucets-are-there-what-is-the-cause-of-the-leaking-faucet","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/yoroow.com\/how-many-faucets-are-there-what-is-the-cause-of-the-leaking-faucet\/","title":{"rendered":"How many faucets are there? What is the cause of the leaking faucet?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Faucets are one of the more common sanitary wares in daily life. There are many types and styles of faucets on the market, which makes the prices of faucets vary greatly. The prices of well-known brand faucets on the market are much higher than those of ordinary faucets. The following is an introduction to several types of faucets and the causes of leaking faucets.<\/p><p>How many faucets are there? What is the cause of the leaking faucet? _1<\/p><p><br>How many faucets are there?<\/p><p>1. Brass<\/p><p>The brass faucet uses a steel mold for gravity casting, and the wall thickness is uniform. This faucet is non-rusty, durable, anti-oxidant, and has a sterilization effect on water.<\/p><p>2. Plastic<\/p><p>Plastic faucets are corrosion-resistant, non-toxic, odorless, light weight, and high pressure resistant. They are a new type of green and environmentally friendly product that meets the national drinking and civil drinking water standards. This green and environmentally friendly product will be a reminder in the faucet industry. It should be promoted vigorously.<\/p><p>3. Stainless steel<\/p><p>Stainless steel faucets do not contain lead and are internationally recognized as a healthy material that can be implanted into the human body. Therefore, kitchen and bathroom products made of stainless steel are slowly becoming popular in European and American countries, but the price of real 304 stainless steel faucets will be higher than that of copper materials. .<\/p><p>4. Zinc alloy<\/p><p>The surface of zinc alloy faucet has white oxide powder, its strength is much worse than that of copper, and its lead content is higher. At present, zinc alloy is mainly used to make the handle of faucet. It is made of zinc alloy die-casting and then chrome-plated. Most faucets on the market The handles are all zinc alloy.<\/p><p>How many faucets are there? What is the cause of the leaking faucet?<\/p><p>Causes of a leaking faucet<\/p><p>1. The faucet is not tightly shut<\/p><p>The faucet is not tightly closed mainly because the internal gasket is damaged. For such problems, you can replace the damaged gasket with a new one. If there is plastic waste in your home, you only need to cut the plastic waste into a gasket the size of a faucet pipe. , Very simple.<\/p><p>2. Water seepage around the valve core of the faucet<\/p><p>This kind of problem is mainly due to excessive &#8220;strength&#8221; when opening, which causes the faucet to loosen. It can be removed and reinstalled. If necessary, glass glue can be used to block it.<\/p><p>3. Water seepage in the bolt gap of the faucet<\/p><p>It can be seen whether the bolts of the faucet are worn out, and if they are, they can be repaired by replacing them.<\/p><p>4. Water seepage at the pipe joint<\/p><p>If there is water seepage at the joints of the pipes, it may be that the nut is loose or rusted. At this time, you can replace the product or add a gasket.&nbsp;<\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Faucets are one of the more common sanitary wares in daily life. There are many types and styles of faucets on the market, which makes the prices of faucets vary greatly. The prices of well-known brand faucets on the market are much higher than those of ordinary faucets. The following is an introduction to several&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_ac